# Project Decisions Log

Project-wide structure, scope, and operating decisions only. Proposition-level state transitions live in `propositions/Pxxx_slug/decisions.md`. Derived-hypothesis state transitions live in `propositions/Pxxx_slug/hypotheses/Hxxx_slug/decisions.md`.

Allowed labels: `OPEN_PROPOSITION`, `SPLIT_PROPOSITION`, `MERGE_PROPOSITION`, `CHANGE_SCOPE`, `CHANGE_PROTOCOL`.

Each entry uses this shape:

```markdown
## YYYY-MM-DD - <DECISION_LABEL>: <short title>

- Scope: project
- Previous status:
- New status:
- Evidence or analysis pointer:
- Rationale:
- Follow-up state change:
```

